3.2 PM10 vs dni tygodnia

Show and hide code 
ops <- 
  ops |> 
  janitor::clean_names() |> 
  mutate(jday = lubridate::yday(date)) |> 
  mutate(
    wday = lubridate::wday(x = date, abbr = T, label = T),
    hour = lubridate::hour(x = date),

      wday == "Mon" ~ "week",
      wday == "Tue" ~ "week",
      wday == "Wed" ~ "week",
      wday == "Thu" ~ "week",
      wday == "Fri" ~ "week",
      wday == "Sat" ~ "weekend",
      wday == "Sun" ~ "weekend"

  ) |> 
  mutate(day_work = as.factor(day_work))
